 This is simply to define a constant, not give it a value. The point 
in this is to use it when including header files i.e.

#ifndef HEADER_INCLUDED	/* If not defined */
#define HEADER_INCLUDED	/* Define it */
#endif

 I think it doesn't have a value (or is maybe 0) as it is not used as 
a value.
 
> How would i convert these values to be used as constants? (if possible):
