Well, for using this and any other tags from the autodocs in Blitz, there are
two ways:

1) To apply the tag when making the GTlist:

  GTTags #GTIN_MaxChars,(number of characters)
  (make the gadget here)

2) To change a tag after window is open and GTlist attached:

  GTSetAttrs Gtlist#,gadID#,#GTIN_MaxChars,(number of characters)


To use a tag that asks for (BOOL)  just use 1 for yes, or 0 for no

To use a tag that asks for a string pointer:

a$="Whatever you want"

then use &a$ for the tag value.
