Thats no problem. I do it like this:

Dim.w myarray(5,7,10)                  ; I used .w as an example

If OpenFile(0,"mydatafile")
   For z=0 to 9
      For y=0 to 6
         For x=0 to 4
            ReadMem 0,&myarray(x,y,z),SizeOf.w       ; Replace the .w in
SizeOf.w with the type you use
         Next                                                                 
         ; for your array
      Next
   Next
Endif

CloseFile 0

Of course you have to write the file the same way,
just replace ReadMem with WriteMem.

