Yes, for this you would use the tags:


DetachGTList 3
GTSetAttrs 3,50,#GTLV_Top,(top item visible in the
listview),#GTLV_Selected,(item to be shown as selected)
AttachGTList 3,2

The one for the top item is not needed for this really - I only use it to make
sure my selected item is shown half-way down the list.



> 
